    <div class="container">
        <h1>PNB Checker tool</h1>
        <p>Select your <b>arrival</b> time (actual) and <b>scheduled</b> departure time to verify your PNB for your location (either <i>pass</i> or <i>fail</i>).

            <form id="time-form">
